c: 7
v: 32
t: "Boola; “Ni wina wakania oburone bwa Nyasaye obwayahelesia Abandu bebe, nende bilia ebilayi mumikabo chichie.? Boola; ebo ni bia balia basuubila nibashili mubulamu bwokhushialo, ne inyanga yeyindukho bilibasa ebiabu bonyene. Endio nilwokhwinoosinjia ebimanyisio biefu khubandu abamanyanga"